data.description:
Welcome to 5420 Lickford Bridge Rd SW. This home boasts 3 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, 2 detached garages, a storm shelter, and over 10 acres! When you enter the home you are greeted by the light filled living room - complete with a stone fireplace. This room opens up to the eat-in kitchen. The large primary suite features a large ensuite bathroom, complete with a double vanity, bathtub, and walk-in shower, as well as a huge walk-in closet! Rounding out the home are two more great bedrooms, another full bathroom, and the laundry room. Outside, you will find a carport and two detached garages - one with 3 spaces and another with 6! The front garage has 220 electrical, water, and is fully insulated. With a huge front deck, a back patio, and 10 acres to roam - you have no shortage of outdoor space to enjoy or hunt! Schedule your showing today.
*Agent is related to sellers but has no personal interest in property.
